Package paint.viewer.panels

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NavigationPanel.Listener
    Listener interface for responding to navigation button events.
    RecordingControlsPanel.Listener
    Defines callback methods for handling user actions triggered by this panel.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NavigationPanel
    A simple reusable navigation component providing First, Previous, Next, and Last buttons for paging or record traversal within the viewer.
    RecordingAttributesPanel
    A Swing panel that presents attributes of a RecordingEntry in tabular form.
    RecordingControlsPanel
    A user interface panel containing interactive controls for managing recordings and grid visualization options within the PAINT viewer.
    SquareGridPanel
    The SquareGridPanel is a graphical component that renders a grid of Square objects, each representing an individual region of interest.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SquareGridPanel.NumberMode
    Enumeration defining numeric display modes for squares.
